==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Convexo-concave
<hw>Con*vex"o-con"cave</hw> <pr>(?⟦or⟧ ?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Convex on one side, and concave on the other. The curves of the
convex and concave sides may be alike or may be different. See
<er>Meniscus</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Convexo-convex</ent>⟦br⟧
